Today, Electric Vehicles (EV) manufacturers are having a tough time getting the cost of electric vehicles low enough to be affordable to the mass market. Highlands provides a solution to that problem by drastically simplifying the drivetrain to decrease manufacturing and assembly time, complexity, and eventually cost.
